&lt;p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">The Heltec WiFi Kit 32 is an IoT development board designed and produced by Heltec Automation and based on the Espressif ESP32. The board includes WiFi, Bluetooth, as well as a 0.96″ 128*64 dot matrix OLED display and a lithium battery management system.&lt;/p>&lt;/body>&lt;/html></description>
